T02TD2008AE:218a-1: shr'i badzra bhee ra ba stu ti /
T02TD2008AE:218a-3: dpal rdo rje 'jigs byed kyi bstod ga dpal rdo rje 'jigs byed la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02TD2008AE:218a-4: h'um 'jam dpal mkha' las byung ba'i gser mdog can //
T02TD2008AE:218a-5: 'jam dpal thugs la chos kun rang bzhin gsal //
T02TD2008AE:218a-6: 'jam dpal gsung gi dbang phyug 'jam dpal dbyangs //
T02TD2008AE:218a-7: 'jam dpal bdag ni re ba'i sems kyis 'dud //
T02TD2008AE:218a-8: thugs mchog 'jam pa'i ngang las ma g-yos kyang //
T02TD2008AE:218a-9: thugs rjes gdug pa 'dul phyir gshin rje'i gshed //
T02TD2008AE:218a-10: 'jigs byed chen po 'jigs pa'i char bstan nas //
T02TD2008AE:218a-11: mi bzad dus mtha'i bskal pa'i me ltar 'bar //
T02TD2008AE:218a-12: zhal gdangs khro gnyer smin ma glog ltar 'gyur //
T02TD2008AE:218a-13: spyan bgrad mche ba gtsigs shing rab tu 'bar //
T02TD2008AE:218a-14: rdo rje'i rta gad drag po ha har bzhad //
T02TD2008AE:218a-15: mkha' 'gro sdud pa'i phem skad gnam du 'don //
T02TD2008AE:218a-16: khros pa'i zhabs chen brdabs pas khams gsum gnon //
T02TD2008AE:218a-17: sdigs mdzub gnam du bsgrengs shing lha chen 'dul //
T02TD2008AE:218a-18: ljags 'dril tshems chen gtsigs shing khrag gis myos //
T02TD2008AE:218a-19: lha dang bcas pa'i 'jig rten zhal du gsol //
T02TD2008AE:218a-20: glang chen ko rlon thod pa'i phreng ba zhags //
T02TD2008AE:218a-21: gcer bu 'jigs byed dbang phyug chen po'i tshul //
T02TD2008AE:218a-22: 'jigs byed ma he khros pa'i zhal gdangs shing //
T02TD2008AE:218a-23: zhal dgu 'bar bas srid pa zad par rngub //
T02TD2008AE:218a-24: 'gro ba sna tshogs 'dul ba'i phyag rgya 'bar //
T02TD2008AE:218a-25: bdud bzhi gnon pa'i zhabs ni brkyang bskum gnas //
T02TD2008AE:218a-26: 'jigs byed chen po'i sku la rtag tu 'dud //
T02TD2008AE:218a-28: g-yas kyi zhal gsum bgrad pa ni //
T02TD2008AE:218a-29: mthing ga dmar dang ser ba'i zhal //
T02TD2008AE:218a-30: g-yon gyi zhal gsum gdangs pa ni //
T02TD2008AE:218b-0: dkar dang dud ka @218b gnag pa'i zhal //
T02TD2008AE:218b-1: dbus kyi zhal gsum 'bar ba ni //
T02TD2008AE:218b-2: khro dang chags dang zhi ba'i tshul //
T02TD2008AE:218b-4: g-yas kyi phyag mtshan bcu drug ni //
T02TD2008AE:218b-5: rdeg cing 'joms pas mtshon cha gdengs //
T02TD2008AE:218b-6: g-yon gyi phyag mtshan bcu drug ni //
T02TD2008AE:218b-7: rol cing stobs pa'i mtshan mas mdzes //
T02TD2008AE:218b-8: brjid rngam zhabs kyi tsham ngam las //
T02TD2008AE:218b-9: g-yas kyi zhabs brgyad bskum pa ni //
T02TD2008AE:218b-10: dregs pa'i lha brgyad thabs kyis 'dul //
T02TD2008AE:218b-11: g-yon gyi zhabs brgyad brkyang ba ni //
T02TD2008AE:218b-12: dregs pa'i lha mo brgyad la rol //
T02TD2008AE:218b-13: 'dod chags chen po gdul ba'i phyir //
T02TD2008AE:218b-14: rtag tu ling+ga rgyas pa'i tshul //
T02TD2008AE:218b-15: drag po'i tshul gyis zhe sdang 'dul //
T02TD2008AE:218b-17: dur khrod chen po'i dkyil 'khor nas //
T02TD2008AE:218b-18: bdud dang gshin rje thabs kyis 'dul //
T02TD2008AE:218b-19: ma mo mkha' 'gro dbang du sdud //
T02TD2008AE:218b-20: dbang sdud khyod la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02TD2008AE:218b-21: dbang phyug chen po'i dkyil 'khor nas //
T02TD2008AE:218b-22: dbang med dad pas 'dus pa dang //
T02TD2008AE:218b-23: ye shes sprul pa'i 'khor gyis bskor //
T02TD2008AE:218b-25: ye shes thugs kyi dkyil 'khor nas //
T02TD2008AE:218b-26: ji lta bur ni sprul gyur kyang //
T02TD2008AE:218b-27: rnam dag dbyings las ma g-yos pa'i //
T02TD2008AE:218b-28: mnyam nyid sku la phyag 'tshal lo //
